  <brief_title>Regulation and Signaling of Red Blood Cell (RBC) Endothelial Nitric Oxide Synthase (eNOS) in Patients With Stable and Unstable Coronary Artery Disease</brief_title>
  <official_title>Regulation and Signaling of RBC-eNOS in Patients With Stable and Unstable Coronary Artery Disease</official_title>
