  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study is measurement of expression and activity of RBC eNOS in different
      clinical cohorts of patients with coronary artery disease and acute coronary syndrome and to
      investigate the importance of the NO-stimulated reaction cascade in terms of sGC and PKG.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
